<footer class="bg-[#f6f4e6] mt-auto">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 px-8 md:px-12 py-16 border-t border-[#dcc0c1]/30 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Brand Section -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="text-xl font-headline font-semibold">
        <img src="/logoDetra.png" alt="Detra logo" class="h-36 w-auto object-contain">
      </div>
      <p class="font-body text-sm text-[#1c1c14]/60 leading-relaxed max-w-xs">
        Avanzando el estandar de la educacion legal y la investigacion academica para una sociedad mas justa e informada.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Links Section -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h5 class="font-label text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-[#2e0007] font-bold">Navegacion</h5>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li>
            <a class="text-[#1c1c14]/60 hover:text-[#550015] hover:underline transition-all font-label text-sm uppercase tracking-widest" href="#">
              Contacto
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a class="text-[#1c1c14]/60 hover:text-[#550015] hover:underline transition-all font-label text-sm uppercase tracking-widest" href="#">
              Politica de Privacidad
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a class="text-[#1c1c14]/60 hover:text-[#550015] hover:underline transition-all font-label text-sm uppercase tracking-widest" href="#">
              Terminos de Servicio
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h5 class="font-label text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-[#2e0007] font-bold">Social</h5>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li>
            <a class="text-[#1c1c14]/60 hover:text-[#550015] hover:underline transition-all font-label text-sm uppercase tracking-widest" href="#">
              LinkedIn
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a class="text-[#1c1c14]/60 hover:text-[#550015] hover:underline transition-all font-label text-sm uppercase tracking-widest" href="#">
              Twitter
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Copyright Section -->
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full text-left md:text-right">
      <div class="text-[#2e0007] font-label text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">
        Excelencia Academica Editorial
      </div>
      <p class="font-label text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-[#1c1c14]/60 mt-8">
        &copy; 2024 DETRA-UNT. Todos los derechos reservados.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
